creator: Sharry Europe
descriptionHtml:
This application is intended for employees that work in 420 Lexington Avenue and their visitors. Important information about the building can be found on the dashboard, which dynamically changes throughout the day. The app allows employees frictionless access into the property and will enable them to invite guests to the property as well. Additional modules are available including, amenity reservations, events, community information, etc.
This app is created in cooperation with SL Green Realty Corp., and is updated regularly. If you have any suggestions for improvement, if you find a bug, or just want to say hello, please write to us at support@sharryapp.com.
descriptionShort: Mobile access and visitor management system
